  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArmoredEnemy, BossEnemy, FastEnemy, FlyingEnemy, StandardEnemy
    public class Enemy
extends SmoothMover
    Enemies try to reach the cosmic secrets. They have to follow the path to the base at the end with the secrets. They spawn if varius different health, speed and path.
